divs: Sighting Details I observed one black triangle with the pulsing redlight behind and the white light on both sides of the red one. This trianglewas silent, travelling from southeast to northwest almost over my home, over 500feet above. I saw 7 black triangles at different intervals travelling west inthe Northern sky. I observed 1 black triangle travelling east in the northernsky, and one black triangle travelling south in the western sky. All thesecrafts had the same dark angled body with the same configuration of lightsbehind. I also observed the diamond object which I have reported previously.
